thread.title: Nicole
thread.title_full: My Corporate Logo reviewed by Nicole

author: Nicole
title: Nicole
text: As a start up small business this was my first experience designing a logo. Overall the experience was good. The process did take longer than I expected. I think some of the confusion we experienced could have been resolved if phone communication was available instead of just email communication. But even with saying that, my team loves our logo and are ready to move to the next step in launching our business.
